    "message": "\nIf you can't make your own dreams come true, maybe find a way to make others come true? Just a thought.\n\nMy life was really shit at one point and what motivated me was the idea that one day somehow i'll make others lives better. Maybe teach music to children from rotten communities and help them reach their dream? \n\nOr become conservationist or environmentalist, you have a history in Biology so maybe you could use that knowledge to help solve the earths problems?\n\nMaybe you should change your life completely, save up and move somewhere where you know help is needed.\n\n Everyone has a lot to offer, even if it takes them a while to realize. \n\nMaybe do some charity work, you'd be surprised how rewarding it is to make others happy, even if there is nothing in it for you. \n\nAre you in a relationship? Maybe you should think about what would make them happy, and make it a goal to make them smile, because that will mean the world to them. Or if not maybe you should go and find the one person you love and tell them that.\n\nGood Luck, I hope everything works out for you, :)",
